          <text>
                    <body>
                              <pb n="1"/>
                              <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>New Orleans</placeName>, <date>April
                                                  6<hi rend="sup">th</hi> 1848</date></p>
                              <p>
                                        <addressee>Revd Isaac Leeser</addressee>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(2)">DSir!</p>
                              <p rend="indent(3)">I beg have to inform you<lb/> that at the annual
                                        Meeting of the Hebrew Benevolent Associa-<lb/>tion of
                                                  <placeName>New Orleans</placeName>, held on
                                                  <date>Sunday March 26<hi rend="sup"
                                                  >th</hi>1848</date>,<lb/> the following Officers,
                                        were elected to serve for the ensuing<lb/> year.</p>
                              <list type="members">
                                        <head>List of members</head>
                                        <item rend="indent(1)"><persName>A Emanuel.</persName>
                                                  President.<persName>M Kursheedt </persName> Vice
                                                  President</item>
                                        <item rend="indent(1)"><persName>David Sanger.</persName>
                                                  Treasurer. And <persName>Leopold Cohn</persName>
                                                  Secretary</item>
                              </list>
                              <p>Board of Managers—<persName>S. Magner</persName>. <persName>A
                                                  Harber</persName>, <persName>E. Jacobs</persName>.
                                                  <persName>G G Levi</persName><lb/> and
                                                  <persName>N. Worms</persName></p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">The anniversary Ball, given in this city on the
                                                  <date>20<hi rend="sup">th</hi><lb/> March
                                                  1848.</date> for the benefit of the association,
                                        was very num-<lb/>erously attended many distinguished
                                        citizens, and dignitaries<lb/> of the state were present on
                                        the, Occasion,</p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">It is gratifying to state, that the affair
                                        passed<lb/> off to the entire <sic>satisfactione</sic> of
                                        all, and much praise<lb/> is due to the <hi rend="underline"
                                                  >committee of arrangement</hi>, for the<lb/>
                                        Splendor and style in which the ball was conducted<lb/> and
                                        their untiring efforts, to give general satisfaction,<lb/>
                                        has been crowned with great success. <sic>the</sic> nett
                                        proceeds<lb/> amounting to Seven Hundred dollars which
                                        amount<lb/> greatly replenishes the exhausted state of the
                                        fund of<lb/> the Society, having expended for charitable
                                        purposes<lb/> Fifteen Hundred Dollars during the passed
                                        year.</p>
                              <pb n="2"/>
                              <p>caused by the raging Epidemic of last summer.</p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">I have the honor to remain with sentiments of
                                        esteem</p>
                              <p rend="indent(5)">Your Very Obt Sevt</p>
                              <p rend="indent(6)">
                                        <persName role="author">L. Cohn</persName>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(6)">Secretary H. B. A.</p>
